result.longName: Shanghai Hajime Advanced Material Technology Co., Ltd.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Shanghai Hajime Advanced Material Technology Co., Ltd. manufactures engineering plastics precision parts and precision molds for passenger cars, commercial vehicles, new energy vehicles, high-end kitchen and bathroom appliances, and other applications. It offers automotive airbag components, engine knock sensors, thermal management modules, plastic tensioner parts, carbon can solenoid valves, quick couplings, electronic water valves, thermoset components, piping components, engine resonator components, filtration system, vehicle heater components, PPS thermal management module components, window seal components, PPS thermal management module components, carbon canister solenoid valve parts, actuator components, electronic water pump component - PPS impellers, split impellers, solenoid valve components, and car tail box buttons. It also offers energy vehicle parts comprising automotive electronic water pumps, stator assemblies, shock absorber parts of hybrid new energy, energy vehicle plastic tensioner wheels, automobile battery cooling systems, and energy capacitor parts. In addition, the company provides hydrant mixing valves, gas and electric water heaters, water toilet deodorizing components, water toilet heating kits, water toilet flowmeters and cushion tanks, toilet solenoid valve, nozzle assemblies, water purifier faucets and bases, warm water toilet bezels, and water toilet instant heating kits. Further, it offers pump guide plates discs, pump impellers, electromagnet parts for industrials, and solenoid valve parts, as well as router, projector, and camera widgets. Shanghai Hajime Advanced Material Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.
